---
title: Mussel Linguine and Roasted Salmon with Herby Garlic Ciabatta
description: Seafood linguine is the best part of an Italian feast. Bright and briny flavours of the sea are balanced with sweet, bursting cherry tomatoes and zesty garlic. Soak up the delicious sauce with herb and garlic ciabatta toasts.
